data.description: Welcome home!  This very well maintained home is move-in ready, in a corner lot, featuring 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, completely remodeled.  Living room with a wood burning cozy brick fireplace.  Kitchen with granite countertops. Enjoy the backyard with a cover patio and pool, ideal to entertain families and friends.  Close to restaurants, schools and major highways.  Make this one your home!  Call me for a private tour.  Don't miss this one!
